About Us
We are a non-profit & non-denomination initiative to bring Buddhism online, 
making it accessible to people of various Buddhist traditions around the world.
Our work relies on dedicated volunteer, and advisor working remotely and online 
in various countries. Together we bring forth our goal of making Buddhism more 
accessible and engage communities for the benefit of all beings.

You may use this app for free, but you maybe optionally sign up for a subscrip-
tion to become a Patron to support the continued development of the app and 
other upcoming app. 
If you want to support our mission - donation & patronage subscription are available.
Please go to “Donate” tab for details – donate via In-App subscription 

Acknowledgement
All the audio recordings and images used in this app were obtained from public 
domain sources. We like to acknowledge and credit the content creator/owner of the 
work we used; their name is mentioned alongside their work/production.
No copyright infringement intended. Please contact us if you need to speak to us.
